Situated near Sheikh Zayed Road, residents of Casa Canal enjoy seamless connectivity to other parts of the emirate. Whether it's reaching Dubai International Airport, Dubai Creek Harbour, or Za'abeel, among other sought-after destinations, travel time by car does not exceed 15 minutes, assuming smooth traffic conditions. A mere 10-minute drive away lies the renowned Downtown Dubai, known for its iconic attractions that make it a national treasure. Within Downtown Dubai, residents can explore the Dubai Mall, Burj Khalifa, The Dubai Fountain, Dubai Opera, and numerous other landmarks.

DAMAC Cavalli Couture is an exclusive and luxurious residential project brought to life by DAMAC Properties, in collaboration with the legendary fashion house of Roberto Cavalli. Nestled along the picturesque banks of the Dubai Water Canal, this project redefines opulent living in one of the most desirable areas of Dubai. With a limited number of super-luxury residences, Cavalli Couture sets a new standard for upscale living, offering residents a harmonious lifestyle with access to key landmarks and a myriad of attractions.
Property Types
Cavalli Couture presents a selection of meticulously designed apartments, including 3, 4, and 5-bedroom units, showcasing high-end design at every turn. The 3-4 bedroom apartments feature floor areas starting at 4,300 sqft, while more spacious 5-bedroom duplexes boast living areas from 8,750 sqft. Each of the 70 super-luxury residences in this 12-story building enjoys unobstructed views of the Dubai Water Canal.
Location
This project is strategically situated on the banks of the Dubai Water Canal, offering breathtaking waterfront views. It also resides within the 64-hectare Safa Park, celebrated for its lush natural surroundings and top-notch entertainment and recreational amenities. The location provides easy access to key landmarks in Dubai.
Amenities
Residents of Cavalli Couture are treated to an array of top-notch amenities that enhance their vibrant and tranquil lifestyle. On the rooftop, a swimming pool and a lounge zone await, where residents can savor exclusive dishes prepared by a chef. The project promises waterfront views of the canal, adding to its allure.
Shopping and Entertainment
The vicinity of Cavalli Couture offers an abundance of shopping and entertainment options. The Dubai Mall, one of the world's largest shopping centers, is nearby, featuring 1,200 retail stores, 200 dining options, and various entertainment activities. City Walk, an outdoor retail complex, provides a plethora of fashion brand stores, restaurants, and entertainment venues, including Roxy Cinemas and The Green Planet, an indoor tropical forest.
Recreation
For sports enthusiasts and nature lovers, the Meydan Academy & Driving Range is just a 15-minute drive away. The Ras Al Khor Wildlife Sanctuary, known for its diverse bird population, offers a unique experience. Additionally, the development is conveniently located near Jumeirah Beach and Sunrise Beach for those seeking seaside leisure.
Pricing and Payment Plan
The starting price for these luxury residences is AED 16,500,000. A flexible payment plan of 70-30 is available, with an initial 70% payment and the remaining 30% to be settled later.
Why Choose DAMAC Cavalli Couture?
DAMAC Cavalli Couture is an epitome of luxury living in the heart of Dubai, combining high-end design, waterfront vistas, and access to a rich array of amenities and entertainment options. This exclusive project promises to redefine the standards of upscale living and offers a unique opportunity for those who seek a harmonious lifestyle in the emirate of Dubai.

Mercedes-Benz Places is a collaborative venture between Binghatti Developers and luxury automotive giant Mercedes-Benz, located in the heart of Downtown Dubai. This iconic residential project features 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments as well as penthouses, soaring to an impressive height of 341 meters across 65 floors, redefining opulence in the city's skyline.
Strategically positioned, the development offers unobstructed views of the renowned Burj Khalifa, surrounded by iconic structures such as the Dubai Mall and the Museum of the Future. The partnership between the developer and Mercedes-Benz is dedicated to a customer-centric approach, prioritizing the needs and desires of future residents.
Architectural excellence is a key highlight, boasting floor-to-ceiling heights of 4.2 meters that provide a sense of spaciousness and luxury. Each unit is adorned with a private pool, offering residents an exclusive retreat within their homes. The panoramic views from every unit facing the Burj Khalifa create an awe-inspiring living environment, incorporating the automotive giant's design philosophy of 'Sensual Purity' to create timeless and beautiful spaces.
The project, a result of meticulous planning and design, incorporates smart home technologies and intelligent mobility solutions, aiming to redefine comfort and convenience in modern living spaces. It envisions a lifestyle that seamlessly combines sophistication with the exclusivity of an oasis.
Key highlights include a premium collection of 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments and penthouses, an astounding elevation of 341 meters across 65 floors, strategic location in Downtown Dubai, private pools in each residence, and adherence to the Mercedes-Benz design philosophy of 'Sensual Purity.'
In summary, Mercedes-Benz Places is an exclusive residential complex embodying ultra-luxury services, a collaboration between renowned developers and the iconic Mercedes-Benz brand, offering a harmonious oasis of serenity, aesthetic appeal, and a lifestyle that seamlessly blends automotive excellence with architectural grandeur.

Imagine waking up to panoramic views of Dubai Creek, the iconic Yacht Club, and the bustling city skyline. Dubai Creek Residences offers an unparalleled waterfront lifestyle, with exclusive one-, two-, and three-bedroom homes set right at the edge of Creek Island.

Immerse yourself in a world of luxury and convenience. Creek Island boasts a stunning Island Park, a serene Creek Beach, and an upscale Yacht Club with 81 berths. Explore the vibrant promenade, filled with art installations, shops, restaurants, and leisure activities. Every day at Dubai Creek Residences is an opportunity to create unforgettable memories.
Indulge in Unmatched Amenities
Enjoy the best of both worlds: the tranquility of waterfront living and the excitement of city life. Dubai Creek Residences offers a range of amenities designed to enhance your lifestyle, including:

Panoramic Creek Views
Exclusive Waterfront Location
Luxurious Apartment Designs
Island Park and Creek Beach
Upscale Yacht Club
Vibrant Promenade with Retail and Dining

Discover Your Dream Home
Dubai Creek Residences is more than just a place to live; it's a lifestyle.

Jumeirah Asora Bay, located in the prestigious La Mer community of Jumeirah First, Dubai, offers an exclusive retreat that epitomizes coastal luxury. Developed by Meraas, this premium project combines modern architecture with the natural beauty of the waterfront, delivering a harmonious blend of elegance and serenity.
Key Features:

Elegant Residences: Offering a selection of 4- to 7-bedroom apartments and penthouses, thoughtfully designed to provide spacious layouts, premium finishes, and breathtaking views of the Arabian Gulf.
Resort-Inspired Amenities: Residents can enjoy private beach access, infinity pools, world-class wellness facilities, and landscaped communal areas, creating an unmatched lifestyle experience.
Prime Coastal Location: Nestled in La Mer, the development offers unparalleled connectivity to Dubai’s best dining, shopping, and leisure destinations, while providing a serene coastal escape.

Jumeirah Asora Bay redefines luxury living with its exclusive homes, exceptional amenities, and iconic location. This is more than just a residential community—it’s a lifestyle crafted for those who desire the best of modern living alongside the beauty of Dubai’s pristine coastline.

Located in the heart of Za’abeel 2, Akala Hotels and Residences by Arada is a striking 50-storey tower that blends luxury living with world-class hospitality. Designed for modern urbanites and global investors, the project features a refined selection of serviced apartments, hotel units, and branded residences—all set against the vibrant backdrop of Dubai’s iconic skyline.
With its proximity to DIFC, Downtown Dubai, and the World Trade Centre, Akala offers seamless connectivity and unmatched convenience. Residents will enjoy state-of-the-art amenities, panoramic city views, wellness and leisure spaces, fine dining, and an elevated sense of privacy.
Whether you're looking for a prestigious address or a high-yield property investment, Akala at Za’abeel 2 delivers on every front—design, location, and lifestyle.
